Hierarchy > Create > 3D Object > Capsule
Hierarchy > Right Click > 3D object > capsule
rename this capsule to Enemy 
set the position of this enemy capsule in front of the character capsule (Ex : x = -0.86 Y : 6 Z 15.5)
create a new folder inside assets (Scripts) and create a script into Scripts Project > Right Click > Create > MonoBehaviour Script 
rename this MonoBehaviour Script folder enemyvisionscript 
open it and copy my enemyvision script and save it(ctrl+s)
drag this script to to enemy capsule
create a new folder inside assets (Metarials) and create a metarial 2 times into Metarial Project > Metarial > Right Click > Create > Metarial
change their names : Detected , Normal
click to new metarial project > metarial > Detected > Surface Inputs > change color to red
click to new metarial project > metarial > Normal > Surface Inputs > change color to green
Hierarchy > Enemy capsulue > Inspector > enemy vision script > drag normal metarial to here  
Hierarchy > Enemy capsulue > Inspector > enemy vision script > drag detected metarial to here  
Hierarchy > Enemy capsulue > Inspector > enemy vision script > Obstacle Mask > Ground(place)
Hierarchy > Enemy capsulue > Inspector > enemy vision script > Player > character 
